t was also the name of the wife of  Henry VI  of England,  Margaret of Anjou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705190,"age":8,"year":"1290","julianDay":2192224,"title":"Jews Expelled From England","description":"After years of anti-Semitic behavior, King Edward I expelled Jews from England in 1290.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Margaretta Bonyngton was born in 1282, in Goodnestone, Kent, England. She married Thomas de Bois in 1307. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1311, at the age of 29."},"et":{"1282–1311":"1282–1311","1280–1311":"1280–1311","1330–1362":"1330–1362","1307–1362":"1307–1362","1311":"1311","1330":"1330","1362":"1362","1282":"1282","1307":"1307","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","Goodnestone, Kent, England":"Goodnestone, Kent, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"fi":{"1282–1311":"1282–1311","1280–1311":"1280–1311","1330–1362":"1330–1362","1307–1362":"1307–1362","1311":"1311","1330":"1330","1362":"1362","1282":"1282","1307":"1307","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","Goodnestone, Kent, England":"Goodnestone, Kent, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"fr":{"1282–1311":"1282–1311","1280–1311":"1280–1311","1330–1362":"1330–1362","1307–1362":"1307–1362","1311":"1311","1330":"1330","1362":"1362","1282":"1282","1307":"1307","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","Goodnestone, Kent, England":"Goodnestone, Kent, Angleterre","Kent, England":"Kent, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Margaretta Bonyngton est née en 1282, à Goodnestone, Kent, Angleterre. Elle a épousé Thomas de Bois en 1307. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée en 1311, à l’âge de 29 ans."},"de":{"1282–1311":"1282–1311","1280–1311":"1280–1311","1330–1362":"1330–1362","1307–1362":